name: Umbrella Adventure - Second Dream - Part 1
description:
-Don't forget the umbrella. -Why would I need one though? -You never know when it might rain. -But I like the rain. -Take the camera too, you'll need it. -What's a camera?

She knew how to operate it. Catching moments in time felt like her second nature in this dreamscape, pointing and clicking and noticing and snapping. She quickly packed her gear and headed towards the nearest city.
